                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre build: &lt;a href=&quot;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/17795/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-reviews/17795/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;sanity-hsm test 111a failed as follows:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;Remove from backend: 0x200000402:0x50:0x0 = /home/autotest/.autotest/shared_dir/2013-08-29/110531-70153027668640/arc1/0050/0000/0402/0000/0002/0000/0x200000402:0x50:0x0
CMD: client-32vm3 /usr/sbin/lctl get_param -n mdt.lustre-MDT0000.hsm.agent_actions | awk &apos;/&apos;0x200000402:0x50:0x0&apos;.*action=&apos;RESTORE&apos;/ {print \$13}&apos; | cut -f2 -d=
Changed after 0s: from &apos;&apos; to &apos;SUCCEED&apos;
Waiting 100 secs for update
&amp;lt;~snip~&amp;gt;
Update not seen after 100s: wanted &apos;FAILED&apos; got &apos;&apos;
 sanity-hsm test_111a: @@@@@@ FAIL: request on 0x200000402:0x50:0x0 is not FAILED 
&lt;/pre&gt;
